    "whoUses": "Nephrologists (kidney specialists), cardiologists, and primary care physicians use this code when treating patients with chronic kidney disease, glomerulonephritis, polycystic kidney disease, or other renal conditions that cause elevated blood pressure. It commonly appears on EOBs for patients with documented kidney disease who are being treated for hypertension as part of their kidney disorder management.",
