    "whoUses": "Cardiologists, interventional cardiologists, and emergency medicine physicians use this code when diagnosing and treating patients with atypical or unusual causes of heart attacks. This code commonly appears on patient EOB statements for those hospitalized with acute cardiac events, as it triggers significant billing and admission documentation.",
