    "whoUses": "Cardiologists and interventional cardiologists use this code when diagnosing patients with persistent chest pain symptoms and evidence of microvascular dysfunction on specialized cardiac testing (such as stress tests or coronary flow reserve measurements). This code appears on EOB statements for patients undergoing cardiology evaluation and management of chronic chest pain syndromes.",
