    "whoUses": "Cardiologists and emergency medicine physicians use this code when diagnosing and managing arrhythmias detected on EKG, Holter monitors, or during patient evaluations. It commonly appears on patient EOBs when procedures like EKGs, stress tests, or cardiac monitoring are performed to evaluate palpitations or irregular heartbeats.",
