    "plainEnglish": "This code means you've had bleeding inside your brain that was not caused by a head injury or trauma. The bleeding occurred in one of the spaces or tissues within the skull, which can be dangerous because blood accumulates and puts pressure on brain tissue. Symptoms can include sudden severe headache, weakness, numbness, difficulty speaking, or loss of consciousness, depending on where and how much bleeding occurred.",
