    "whoUses": "Neurologists, emergency medicine physicians, and stroke specialists use this code when documenting acute ischemic stroke cases in hospital settings and during follow-up care. It commonly appears on EOB statements for patients hospitalized with acute stroke requiring imaging, intervention, and rehabilitation services.",
