    "plainEnglish": "This code means you've had bleeding inside your brain (not from an injury), and you're now dealing with long-term effects from that event. The bleeding has healed, but you may experience lasting problems like weakness, speech difficulties, memory issues, or other neurological effects depending on where the bleeding occurred. Doctors use this code when they know you had a brain bleed but aren't documenting the specific ongoing problem you're experiencing.",
