    "whoUses": "Neurologists, physiatrists (rehabilitation doctors), neuropsychologists, and primary care physicians use this code when documenting a patient's recovery or ongoing challenges after an ischemic stroke. It commonly appears on EOB statements for patients receiving rehabilitation services, cognitive therapy, or mental health support following their stroke event.",
