    "whoUses": "This code is primarily used by cardiologists, cardiothoracic surgeons, and emergency medicine physicians when diagnosing and treating aortic dissection. It commonly appears on EOB statements for patients hospitalized with this acute vascular emergency, as it typically requires imaging (CT scan) and often emergency surgery or intensive medical management.",
