    "whoUses": "Vascular surgeons, interventional radiologists, and hematologists use this code when managing patients with chronic venous thromboembolism in the neck region. It appears on EOB statements when patients undergo imaging (ultrasound or CT), anticoagulation therapy, or interventional procedures to address the clotting, and is commonly seen in patients with central lines, cancer, or prior neck trauma.",
