    "whoUses": "Obstetrician-gynecologists, midwives, and general practitioners use this code when managing vulval varices, particularly in pregnant patients where the condition is common due to increased venous pressure. It occasionally appears on EOB statements, especially during pregnancy-related care or when variceal complications require treatment or monitoring.",
