    "plainEnglish": "This code describes a problem with your lymphatic system—the network of vessels and nodes that help fight infection and manage fluid in your body—but doctors haven't identified a specific cause or type of disorder. You might experience swelling in your arms, legs, or other areas, feel tired, or notice enlarged lumps under your skin, but the exact condition causing these symptoms hasn't been pinpointed or documented in detail.",
