    "whoUses": "Cardiac surgeons, cardiothoracic surgeons, and operating room teams use this code when documenting complications during heart procedures like bypass surgery, valve repair, or transplants. This code commonly appears on hospital bills and EOB statements for patients who experienced this complication during their cardiac surgery.",
